name: World update version 2К21 or Cryptophenix
description:
We are on the threshold of a new age of finance and art.
No fear, no prejudice, no trick.
Yes determination, yes knowledge, yes inspiration.

Space decides what the future will be

Art minted on tezos - in favor of greener NFT

Together with the NFT, the collector takes the VR file and downloads it to his device. The owner comes inside the art and sees what is inaccessible to the ordinary viewer.
